- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses the functional package management paradigm, which is related to programming languages and their design. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions scientific software, which may include machine learning libraries and tools. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries): The paper discusses sharing and reproducibility among researchers, which is related to digital libraries and their management.
